{"route":{"route":"/posts/3a1d136/","outputPath":"posts/3a1d136/index.html","kind":"post","title":"使用GVT-g显卡虚拟化","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"3a1d136"}},"description":"为内核添加参数 比如grub在/etc/default/grub的GRUB CMDLINE LINUX DEFAULT=中添加 启用modules 在/etc/mkinitcpio.conf的MODULES=()中添加: 然后运行,我用的zen内核所以是linux zen,默认内核是linux 重启计算机 查看/sys","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/使用GVT-g显卡虚拟化.md","route":"/posts/3a1d136/","abbrlink":"3a1d136","title":"使用GVT-g显卡虚拟化","date":"2021-01-17 20:53:29","updated":"2021-01-17 20:53:29","tags":["Linux","qemu","GVT-g","intel"],"categories":["Linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"为内核添加参数\">为内核添加参数</h2>\n<p>比如<code>grub</code>在<code>/etc/default/grub</code>的<code>GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT=</code>中添加</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">intel_iommu</span>=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">on</span> i915.enable_gvt=<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> i915.enable_guc=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"启用modules\">启用modules</h2>\n<p>在<code>/etc/mkinitcpio.conf</code>的MODULES=()`中添加:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># linux 5.14后，arch的linux内核模块已经不会勾选vfio-mdev，自测不影响gvt-g</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">kvmgt vfio vfio-iommu-type1s</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后运行,我用的zen内核所以是linux-zen,默认内核是linux</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> mkinitcpio -p linux-zen</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>重启计算机</p>\n<p>查看<code>/sys/devices/pci0000:00/0000:00:02.0/mdev_supported_types</code>可以看见类似如下的目录</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ls /sys/devices/pci${GVT_DOM}/$GVT_PCI/mdev_supported_types</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">i915-GVTg_V5_1  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Video memory: &lt;512MB, 2048MB&gt;, resolution: up to 1920x1200</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">i915-GVTg_V5_2  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Video memory: &lt;256MB, 1024MB&gt;, resolution: up to 1920x1200</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">i915-GVTg_V5_4  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Video memory: &lt;128MB, 512MB&gt;, resolution: up to 1920x1200</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">i915-GVTg_V5_8  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Video memory: &lt;64MB, 384MB&gt;, resolution: up to 1024x768</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>向create文件中写入uuid(自己生成)就会创建相应的虚拟显卡</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_GUID</span>&quot;</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/sys/devices/pci<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${GVT_DOM}</span>/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_PCI</span>/mdev_supported_types/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_TYPE</span>/create&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>移除</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">echo</span> 1 &gt; /sys/bus/pci/devices/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_PCI</span>/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_GUID</span>/remove</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"qemu添加钩子-启动虚拟机时自动创建虚拟显卡\">qemu添加钩子, 启动虚拟机时自动创建虚拟显卡</h2>\n<p><code>/etc/libvirt/hooks/qemu</code>中, 沒有则自己创建</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">#!/bin/bash</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">GVT_PCI=&lt;GVT_PCI&gt; <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 这里为显卡的地址, 比如 0000:00:02.0</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">GVT_GUID=&lt;GVT_GUID&gt; <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 这里为自己生成的uuid</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">MDEV_TYPE=&lt;GVT_TYPE&gt; <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 这里为要使用的虚拟的类型, 比如 i915-GVTg_V5_8</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DOMAIN=&lt;DOMAIN name&gt; <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># qemu虚拟机的名字</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$#</span> -ge 3 ]; <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">then</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> [ <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$1</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$DOMAIN</span>&quot;</span> -a <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;prepare&quot;</span> -a <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$3</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;begin&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">then</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_GUID</span>&quot;</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;/sys/bus/pci/devices/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_PCI</span>/mdev_supported_types/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$MDEV_TYPE</span>/create&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">elif</span> [ <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$1</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$DOMAIN</span>&quot;</span> -a <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;release&quot;</span> -a <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$3</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;end&quot;</span> ]; <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">then</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">echo</span> 1 &gt; /sys/bus/pci/devices/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_PCI</span>/<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$GVT_GUID</span>/remove</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fi</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">fi</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这样启动虚拟机时会自动创建, 停止后会自动删除</p>\n<h2 id=\"生成虚拟机配置\">生成虚拟机配置</h2>\n<p>可以使用<code>virt-manager</code>先生成一个虚拟机, 再修改相应的配置, 默认配置文件在<code>/etc/libvirt/qemu/</code><br>\n需要添加/修改的配置:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:commandline</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;-set&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;device.hostdev0.x-igd-opregion=on&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;-set&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;device.hostdev0.ramfb=on&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;-set&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:arg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;device.hostdev0.driver=vfio-pci-nohotplug&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:env</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;MESA_LOADER_DRIVER_OVERRIDE&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;i965&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">&lt;!--intel启用OpenGL可能会花屏, 不会就不要加这一条--&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">qemu:commandline</span>&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>hostdev配置可以在添加硬件(PCI HOST Devices)的界面直接修改xml, 更方便一点</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">hostdev</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;subsystem&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;mdev&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">managed</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;no&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">model</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;vfio-pci&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">display</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;on&#x27;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">source</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">address</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">uuid</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;93397e71-15bf-4889-98b7-aa2d735e6260&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">source</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">address</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;pci&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">domain</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;0x0000&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">bus</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;0x00&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">slot</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;0x09&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">function</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;0x0&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">hostdev</span>&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">video</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">model</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;none&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">video</span>&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">graphics</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;spice&#x27;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">listen</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;none&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">image</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">compression</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;off&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">jpeg</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">compression</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;never&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">zlib</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">compression</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;never&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">playback</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">compression</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;off&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">streaming</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">mode</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;off&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">gl</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">enable</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;yes&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">rendernode</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;/dev/dri/by-path/pci-0000:00:02.0-render&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">graphics</span>&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">vcpu</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">placement</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;static&#x27;</span>&gt;</span>2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">vcpu</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">cputune</span>&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">vcpupin</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">vcpu</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">cpuset</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">vcpupin</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">vcpu</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;1&#x27;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">cpuset</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;2&#x27;</span>/&gt;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">cputune</span>&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"结尾\">结尾</h2>\n<p>启动虚拟机后, 进入虚拟机安装相应的显卡驱动就行了.<br>\n这样就快很多了, 比软件渲染快多了, 这样用linux也能愉快的使用其他系统了.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Intel_GVT-g\">Intel_GVT-g</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@langleyhouge/%E8%AE%A9-kvm-%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84-windows-%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E6%8F%92%E4%B8%8Agvt-g-%E7%9A%84%E7%BF%85%E8%86%80-ac0ac28b73b8\">让 KVM 上的 Windows 虚拟机插上GVT-g 的翅膀</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.libvirt.org/hooks.html\">libvirt hooks</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.bepbep.co/posts/gvt/\">Intel Gvt</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"为内核添加参数","text":"为内核添加参数","level":2},{"id":"启用modules","text":"启用modules","level":2},{"id":"qemu添加钩子-启动虚拟机时自动创建虚拟显卡","text":"qemu添加钩子, 启动虚拟机时自动创建虚拟显卡","level":2},{"id":"生成虚拟机配置","text":"生成虚拟机配置","level":2},{"id":"结尾","text":"结尾","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"3a1d136","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}